{"tid":702000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛津大學報告：近半港人憂網上論政惹麻煩","createTime":"2018-06-14T14:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T02:53:38.000Z","uid":20058,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9548eb6f7095bdf9c99823bd2e810ac371236e91","tid":702000,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"牛津大學路透社新聞研究所。周四（14日）公布第7份「電子新聞研究」年度報告，當中全球使用Facebook獲取新聞資訊人數愈來愈少。在提及香港章節時，報告指48%港人受訪者擔心網上論政會遭當局惹麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報告利用民調網站YouGov，在今年1月至2月間。訪問37個國家和地區中約7.4萬名民眾，了解各人使用互聯網看新聞的習慣。報告問及受訪者是否擔心網上平台論政會遭當局惹麻煩，其中香港表示擔心的，在2016名本地受訪者中佔65%，在37個國家中排行第7。<br />\n<br />\n報告結果顯示，雖然Facebook現時依然是全球人們最主要接受新聞資訊的平台，但比例已由2016年的42%，下跌至今年的36%。相比之下，WhatsApp、Instagram和Snapchat則有所上升，其中WhatsApp平均增幅最大，四年內增加兩倍，達至今年的15%。<br />\n<br />\n然而上述情況並不適用於香港。在報告講述香港現況的章節中，港人最主要接受新聞資訊平台，頭6位依次是Facebook、WhatsApp、微信、Instagram、Facebook Messenger和Line。當中使用Facebook看新聞的人數佔56%，較去年上升2%。Whatsapp則佔38%，較去年下跌2%。"},{"pid":"080d23d09acfcceb740f79b5b8a152dd52097d44","tid":702000,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528973053013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528973053013&d=0Y3mLRbNltT6Qu%2BdO6JA6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e570f643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528973053013&h=f2035236\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528973053013</a>"},{"pid":"ae04a5c49af157b2a14b7ae1ce842769f0ecf22d","tid":702000,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7972a46bc95b2edbc5f7f261de739670f14b7ef3","tid":702000,"uid":123786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1587ae3aee69a5e3ce87ba7f9676d46d2c6d58a6","tid":702000,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"中國排第幾？"}]}